Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.94,text,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.00,text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是宾齐托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.88,text,,0,0,0,,我来接人了
