Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.88,text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  在这里等就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.09,text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作做的习惯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.00,text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.93,text,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点独当一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.84,text,,0,0,0,,让我老公轻松点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:37.53,text,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:39.03,text,,0,0,0,,宾齐在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:39.94,text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.64,text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了 安东尼奥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.58,text,,0,0,0,,要好好学习
